  ('medical-tech-moex-16387', 'medical-tech', 'medical-tech-moex-098-9168e375', 'sub-medical-tech-03', NULL, 'single_choice', '某78歲男性病人，因有貧血、容易感染、受傷後不容易止血的症狀到醫院看病，全血計數的結果發 現其紅血球：9.8 g/dL；白血球：1.3×109/L與血小板：38×109/L，血液抹片觀察到嗜中性白血球出現 低顆粒性與疑似Pelger-Huët的現象，這個病人很可能得到下列何種疾病？', '["急性淋巴性白血病（Acute lymphocytic leukemia）", "毛樣細胞白血病（Hairy cell leukemia）", "慢性骨髓性白血病（Chronic myeloid leukemia）", "骨髓異形成症候群（Myelodysplastic syndrome）"]'::jsonb, 0, NULL, FALSE, 'official', TRUE, 1, '{"parser_version": "moex_license_v1.0", "parsed_at": "2026-04-25T07:17:04+00:00", "source_pdf_sha1": "d8700998d574", "answer_pdf_sha1": null, "source_family": "moex-gov-tw", "moex": {"exam_code": "098140", "c": "108", "s": "2001", "q": "1"}, "raw_section_label": "本試題為單一選擇題", "subject": "臨床血液學與血庫學", "year": "098", "exam_name": "098年第二次醫事人員、中醫師、心理師、營養師、醫師分試 、法醫師", "original_question_number": 32, "answer_corrected": false, "flags": ["answer_missing"], "slug": "mt", "db_exam_id": "medical-tech"}'::jsonb, NULL)
